title: The Ranchers (Time-Life, The Old West Series).pdf
description:
Pdf / English / 1977 Time life / 240 pages / 34.6 MB

Describes in text and illustrations the development of large ranches in the western plains, the impact of these establishments on the economy of the area, their organization, and some famous ranches and their owners.

The book has a lot of history in it. I enjoy reading about the Old West. Also, I learn about other Ranchers who are not so famous with Hollywood
